Text: xmas catalog cover just came outhey guess what some of you may remember that neiman marcus commissioned me to design the cover of the xmas catalog this year the th anniversary of their xmas catalog along with my wonderful friend patrick long well i did the frontcover art and he did the backcover art and so well its out i like the cover well enough but i REALLY like the hideous xmas crap they put our designs on you too can check out the crap at dont miss the sweaters on page i also think the delightful cover art musical tree topiary on page is a steal at im also keen on the xmas cover art snow globe for it plays white xmas and etc and etc xo merry xmas colleen Do You Yahoo Get email alerts NEW webcam video instant messaging with Yahoo Messenger

location scout for free on a short independant film that my friend joe bini is directing and we need a couple of interior shots that would take one day to film would you be interested in letting us also it will probably be a cool little film as werner herzog is doing the voice over for sure and may good possibility play the lead there would be no payment for your graciousness but you would get a copy of the film and an invite to the premier it will hopefully enter some film festivals thanks for letting me know if youre interested and kisses to both of you colleen Do You Yahoo Make
